# Project rules

Read these at the start of every task:

- **.aidescription** — AI agent instructions, doc rules, code standards, Git workflow (including "Clean code (must follow)")
- **docs/context.txt** — Open conversations, restrictions, DB structure, next steps
- **docs/requirements.md** — Feature checklist (when implementing features)

Follow clean-code rules in .aidescription: use atoms consistently (no raw button/input/label); update docs/architecture/ when adding major structure.
